@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
actor User
participant "Web Interface" as Web
participant "Input Validation" as Valid
participant "Crop Recommendation" as Crop
participant "Fertilizer Suggestion" as Fert
participant "Disease Detection" as Disease
participant "Weather API" as Weather
participant "Data Sources\n(CSV/Dicts)" as Data
participant "ML Model (Random Forest)" as ML
participant "DL Model (ResNet9)" as DL

' === Flow 1: Crop Recommendation ===
== Crop Recommendation Flow ==

User -> Web: Enter soil parameters
activate Web
Web -> Valid: Validate input (Internal Logic)
activate Valid

Valid --> Web: Input validated
deactivate Valid

Web -> Crop: Submit N, P, K, pH, rainfall, city
activate Crop

Crop -> Weather: Fetch weather data
activate Weather
Weather --> Crop: Return temperature, humidity
deactivate Weather

Crop -> ML: Process 7 features
activate ML
ML --> Crop: Predicted crop
deactivate ML

Crop --> Web: Show recommendation
deactivate Crop

Web --> User: Display crop result
deactivate Web

' === Flow 2: Fertilizer Suggestion ===
== Fertilizer Suggestion Flow ==

User -> Web: Enter N, P, K levels and crop
activate Web

Web -> Valid: Validate NPK values
activate Valid

Valid --> Web: Input validated
deactivate Valid

Web -> Fert: Submit current NPK and crop
activate Fert

Fert -> Data: Read optimal NPK (fertilizer.csv)
activate Data
Data --> Fert: Return optimal NPK
deactivate Data

Fert -> Fert: Calculate nutrient deficit

Fert -> Data: Get advice (fertilizer_dic)
activate Data
Data --> Fert: Return suggestions
deactivate Data

Fert --> Web: Show fertilizer advice
deactivate Fert

Web --> User: Display fertilizer result
deactivate Web

' === Flow 3: Disease Detection ===
== Disease Detection Flow ==

User -> Web: Upload plant image
activate Web

Web -> Valid: Validate image file
activate Valid
Valid --> Web: File validated
deactivate Valid

Web -> Disease: Submit image
activate Disease

Disease -> Disease: Preprocess image

Disease -> DL: Classify disease
activate DL
DL --> Disease: Disease result (38 classes)
deactivate DL

Disease -> Data: Get disease info (disease_dic)
activate Data
Data --> Disease: Treatment recommendations
deactivate Data

Disease --> Web: Show disease result
deactivate Disease

Web --> User: Display disease diagnosis
deactivate Web

@enduml
